WEBVTT

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:03.776
A leader is steady, firm,
decisive, unwavering.

00:00:03.800 --> 00:00:06.256
Never let 'em see you sweat,
always have an answer.

00:00:06.280 --> 00:00:09.040
[The Way We Work]

00:00:10.600 --> 00:00:14.496
My name is Dan, I'm a partner
at a global creative consultancy.

00:00:14.520 --> 00:00:17.296
But there's another side to me:

00:00:17.320 --> 00:00:18.616
Carrie Dragshaw,

00:00:18.640 --> 00:00:20.536
the character I created on Instagram.

00:00:20.560 --> 00:00:25.176
As I thought about my double life,
I couldn't help but wonder ...

00:00:25.200 --> 00:00:28.536
When your true self
is a little nontraditional,

00:00:28.560 --> 00:00:31.240
how much of it can you really
bring to the office?